Very clean and comfortable rooms.	This marriott is in a nice downtown location, and could be a great hotel with a major rennovation.	The hotel has been well maintained and the service was optimal!	The staff is friendly, courteous and professional.	The room was clean and large!	The room was big, clean and the pillows to die for.	Staff were very helpful.	It is clean and very spacious hotel in downtown LA.	The swimming pool at the hotel is great.	The rooms are well appointed and clean, and the service is as usual.